e-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-00226d86-c89e-44d9-8d7e-7d5fecd7b943\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-430ed7f0-14e1-4005-b4a7-4f755a4347b4\" style=\"color:#ff0010;background-color:#ffffff;\">다시 한번 감사의 인사드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-41af83f4-1194-44fa-b635-1d687775a753\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-06fd955b-16c1-4428-96e2-400d859353e2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-aa2d94ef-881d-4b48-94e4-2c7f7f40f91b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d364a400-d6f0-4226-aaf4-e88ef7c5efe9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a829f958-cdac-4580-8403-54a2cabb16f4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-39a34625-6a55-4ce2-a5a6-8362315ee6ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가장 기본이기는 하지만</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-13a29f92-1fd5-4657-9e1d-089982db3c71\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-07930997-6ee4-4cd7-a86a-439ba6e346cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">도무송(톰슨)작업시에는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d0916d04-152a-49e6-892b-da788fd386ab\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f6630fa3-44b8-43cb-8063-cd5053279821\" style=\"color:#555555;\">방향을 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-eee6a8d1-f1e2-4127-ae7c-777096b7fc72\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>반대 방향으로</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-80e4662a-777f-48b1-839a-627f3ff85544\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e3575dc5-0021-4e61-b05f-a021750e4464\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인하셔야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9e64b810-5bbb-4126-8201-dd9c63054686\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-10ab961e-374d-4b92-aa95-ea8be26b26ee\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그렇게 앞, 뒤를 맞춰야 톰슨 모양이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-46b578fc-f64e-4b28-8139-e779223128f8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e9c3be64-bbc7-4776-870c-81083672e5bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제대로 제작될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6792b45f-85f1-45a6-979b-0251c25764b0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-848b81f8-b99b-4f2c-b658-61287e1b6af5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-dfcad7d4-66ec-4031-9e7e-5396bef311dc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223726790791/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-595ece68-8d1f-464f-8698-164c3d6ffe19\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-14e29593-caa2-4b05-8fb7-737037a83212\" style=\"color:#555555;\">도무송작업시 주의할 점은 너무 얇거나 두꺼운 면 작업이 어렵다는 점입니다. 특히 100g 모조지를 도무송작업을 할 때는 각별한 주의를 기울어야 사고를 예방할 수 있습니다. 최소한 150g 이상을 추천드립니다. 이 정도의 두께여야 도무송에서도 말림 현상이나 뜯김 현상이 방지될 수 있습니다. 특히 완칼(완전히 칼을 넣어서 모양을 뜯어내는 경우)의 경우는 종이가 얇으면 작업이 어렵습니다. 주의하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e829b315-5967-4baf-a55f-a60904282c50\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e06f2290-f7e7-40dc-a697-a721b5e226a1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b30870fd-c8a6-47de-b2cc-4e0990f4e98f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223726790791/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5982bddf-e0a4-4b6e-9db9-438c996cd293\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-m